/**
 * @enum PrivateTxState  @interface PrivateTxStatus  @interface RelayResponse  @description Transaction State Types
 *
 * - UNCHECKED -> Tx status has not been checked and there's no information about it. - PROCESSING -> Tx checks are in place until a resolution happens: OK, INDETERMINATE, ERROR. - OK -> Relay received the Tx && all downstream miners accepted without complains && tx mined successfully - INDETERMINATE -> Relay received correctly the Tx && at least one miner accepted the TX && TX potentially mineable - ERROR -> Relay haven't received the TX || none of the miners accepted the Tx || Tx was not mined successfully
 *
 * /**
 *
 * @export  @enum {number}
 */
members.name: PrivateTxState
